targets.rawQuery:
SELECT distinct time, vehicleName
    FROM "FleetWiseDatabase".FleetWiseTable
    WHERE time >= ago(5m)
    AND (measure_value::double) >= 1
    AND measure_name = 'Vehicle.Powertrain.Battery.hasActiveDTC'

SELECT measure_value::double, time FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE campaignName = 'fww_continuous'
  AND measure_name = 'Vehicle_Powertrain_Battery_CellTemp01'
  AND sel_entity= '${sel_entity}'
  AND time >= ago(15m)

SELECT measure_value::double, time FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE campaignName = 'fww_continuous'
  AND measure_name = 'Vehicle_Powertrain_Battery_CellTemp02'
  AND sel_entity= '${sel_entity}'
    AND time >= ago(15m)
LIMIT 100
